                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A ferrofluid magneto-cluster can attach itself to any creature its size or larger that has the tech trait or is wearing or wielding items with the tech trait. This is similar to Grab, but the ooze moves with that creature rather than holding it in place.</p>\n<p>As long as the ooze is attached, it's @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Off-Guard], and the creature it's attached to must succeed at a @Check[flat|dc:11] to Interact with items with the tech trait. On a failure, the item becomes attached to the ooze (treat as if being held by the ooze).</p>"
